						               													<description>&amp;quot;Ever since you became aware of that laptop, and the stolen data held within it, you have been caught up in a dangerous game of cat and mouse. The company, from whom the data has been stolen, are offering a substantial reward for return of their laptop; a reward some people are willing to kill for.  &amp;#10;If you are to stay alive, you will need rely on the support of emergency services, acquire weapons to protect yourself, and hope that your mysterious guardian angel is watching over you.&amp;#10;So find the laptop and keep hold of it until the end of the day to claim your reward&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Pursuit, is a fast paced card game for which is best with 3 or more players, but can be played with 2 people.&amp;#10;Players will take it in turns to draw a card, or play a card, trying to acquire the Target Card (a laptop containing stolen data). Once a player has possession of the Target Card they will soon discover that keeping hold of it is a different challenge as their opponents steal, and attack, to gain the advantage.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
